Users must be able to borrow books
When user borrows books the quanity must be - 1
When quantity reaches zero, program must notify user and not allow them to borrow


ISBN is unique identifier
No need to use objects and classes

Functionality 
	- Small libary of three books, can be hardcoded
	- Implement function to provide details, format output ie. Book Title: etc
	- Implement function to add new book, ask for details and how many copies
	- If ISBN already exists, provide error
	- Implement function to borrow book, decrease quanity by - 1
	- Implement function to search library
	- Include error checking, letter instead of number etc
	- Use comments in code
	